Original Data Attribution

The color naming data is derived from the "Many Languages, Many Colors" research
project by the UW Interactive Data Lab:

  Younghoon Kim, Kyle Thayer, Gabriella Silva Gorsky, and Jeffrey Heer
  "Color Names Across Languages: Salient Colors and Term Translation in 
  Multilingual Color Naming Models"
  EuroVis 2019

  Project: https://uwdata.github.io/color-naming-in-different-languages/
  Paper: http://idl.cs.washington.edu/papers/multi-lingual-color-names/
  Source: https://github.com/uwdata/color-naming-in-different-languages

Please cite the original paper if you use this data in published research.
